ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後因為未過保，所以成部換過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就白癡 我部部都用水濕塊布去抺個mon 咁一定有水走入個槽位 又唔見其他非iphone手機有事<br />\n<br />\n啲藍精靈次次懶無辜咁話我個情況係咁耐以黎第一次見，根本就係常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2466bc5eb1525aca765ad1da4fe7aa69d65dba","tid":302571,"uid":96089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:32:40.000Z","msg":"拎去Hysan Apple store 整<br />\n應該入咗塵塞住咗<br />\n佢會搵嘢幫你吸返出黎<br />\n半個鐘內搞掂唔洗錢"},{"pid":"4ea5ae0861236c76f9db80852789380964c79d42","tid":302571,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎去Hysan Apple store 整<br />\n應該入咗塵塞住咗<br />\n佢會搵嘢幫你吸返出黎<br />\n半個鐘內搞掂唔洗錢</blockquote><br />\n過保都可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3525dbff08498659feb620b38a4a8fcfc2f9025","tid":302571,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"得咁少人壞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e6fd33d0dd402703de4c314570b63af8e43c56","tid":302571,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"壞左好鳩耐<br />\n<br />\n播出黎又無事<br />\n<br />\n係伏係耳仔聽就超細聲<br />\n<br />\n點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53750baf734f904e28ead09791d11a9c858e3d95","tid":302571,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壞左好鳩耐<br />\n<br />\n播出黎又無事<br />\n<br />\n係伏係耳仔聽就超細聲<br />\n<br />\n點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問過整一整收成五百幾 跟住隔三個月又壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d4a505de7325f78d7adbe195551bc23f9aac86","tid":302571,"uid":8375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:14:00.000Z","msg":